tipoint, multipolyline, multipolygon, shape or point collection"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that is specified is silently ignored."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter\/addAnnotation:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter\/addannotation:"]}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapSnapshotter(im)addAnnotation:","symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotation:"}],"title":"addAnnotation:"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Adds an annotation to the snapshotter."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter"]]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshot":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshot","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"An image generated by a snapshotter object.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapSnapshot"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshot","title":"MLNMapSnapshot","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"title":"MapLibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPointCollection":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpointcollection","title":"MLNPointCollection","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNPointCollection"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"disconnected vertices, specified as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"type":"text","text":" instances. The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"points in the collection may be related but are not connected spatially. For"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"example, you could use a point collection to represent all the trees in an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"orchard."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotter/addAnnotation:":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Adds an annotation to the snapshotter."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotation:"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter\/addannotation:","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter\/addAnnotation:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotation:"}],"title":"addAnnotation:"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotOptions":{"title":"MLNMapSnapshotOptions","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotOptions","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapSnapshotOptions","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotoptions","abstract":[{"text":"The options to use when creating images with the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPolyline":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" object represents a shape consisting of two or more vertices,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"specified as ","type":"text"},{"code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" instances, and the line segments that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"connect them. For example, you could use an polyline to represent a road or the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"path along which something moves.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNPolyline"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","title":"MLNPolyline","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolyline"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolyline":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"polylines. For example, you could use a multipolyline shape to represent both","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"sides of a divided highway (dual carriageway), excluding the median (central","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"reservation): each carriageway would be a distinct ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" object.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolyline","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","title":"MLNMultiPolyline","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMultiPolyline"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate":{"abstract":[{"text":"Optional methods about significant events when creating a snapshot using an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" object.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotterdelegate","role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotter":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapSnapshotter"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" generates static raster images of the map. Each snapshot"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"image depicts a portion of a map defined by an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotOptions","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you provide. The snapshotter generates an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshot","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"asynchronously, calling "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" methods if defined, then"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"passing it into a completion handler once tiles and other resources needed for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the snapshot are finished loading."}],"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNMapSnapshotter","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","title":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation"}}}